\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

, and a probability 
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

 is a function from 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ H,T\right\} $
\end_inset

 to 
\begin_inset Formula $\left[0,1\right]$
\end_inset

 with the total probability one, i.e., 
\begin_inset Formula $q\left(H\right)+q\left(T\right)=1$
\end_inset

.
