\begin_inset Formula $\ff{p}$
\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

For example, consider a Hermitian matrix
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{H}_{3}$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathbf{H}_{3}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
